1
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:46,640
One times one is one.

2
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:49,160
Two times two is four.

3
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:51,240
Three times three is nine.

4
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:53,000
Four times four is sixteen.

5
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:57,640
Five times five...

6
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:04,440
Yuanyuan...

7
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,200
I forgot.

8
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,560
Jingyuan,

9
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,320
although he is very mean with his words,

10
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,840
is really good to Ayan.

11
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:26,490
It's as if he knew he was going to leave.

12
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,200
He prepared so many toys for him.

13
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:32,759
Yeah.

14
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,600
Axuan,

15
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:40,800
if one day,

16
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,600
I...

17
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,320
What is it?

18
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,320
Nothing.

19
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,120
The story has reached its end.

20
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,020
Jingyuan has left.

21
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,320
Am I going to leave too?

22
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,560
At some point

23
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,640
that even I can't anticipate.

24
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,840
Yuanyuan.

25
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,720
Why are you ignoring me?

26
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,810
What did you call me?

27
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,079
Yuanyuan.

28
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,000
What about me?

29
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,480
You are Yuanyuan too.

30
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,120
Both of you are Yuanyuan.

31
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:27,160
Ayan has two Yuanyuans.

32
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,360
Axuan.

33
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,160
Yuanyuan.

34
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,560
Why did that Yuanyuan leave?

35
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:56,240
I thought human partings and reunions were like the wind,

36
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:59,320
ending in nothing but a long sleep.

37
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:02,360
But in this bittersweet virtual world,

38
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:05,040
in this supposedly cold palace,

39
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,920
I feel a sincere and passionate vitality.

40
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,000
At this moment,

41
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:14,040
it feels like I'm truly looking at the human world.

42
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,040
Ayan.

43
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:18,680
That Yuanyuan didn't leave.

44
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,160
And I won't leave either.

45
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,920
Lie down, and I'll tell you a story, okay?

46
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:26,920
Okay.

47
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:33,240
User Cangyue Xinglan detected.

48
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:35,760
Character goal 100% completed.

49
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,720
Main quest of the game completed.

50
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,440
About to exit the virtual world.

51
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:41,280
Please get ready.

52
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:06,560
Ah Xuan.

53
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,680
Ah Xuan.

54
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,320
Cangyue.

55
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:13,160
Goodbye, Si Xingxuan.

56
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:35,120
Congratulations. The project experience is successfully completed.

57
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,570
What kind of partnership should we switch to?

58
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,120
What partnership?

59
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,240
A lifelong one.

60
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,800
Child-stealing dog.

61
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,560
I didn't.

62
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,640
You did.

63
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,490
I really didn't.

64
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:43,560
Which is sweeter, the grapes or me?
